snippet.title: Paper Mario: The Thousand-Year Door - Nintendo Direct 9.14.2023
snippet.description:
Paper Mario: The Thousand-Year Door from the Nintendo GameCube system will return with enhanced graphics for Nintendo Switch on May 23, 2024! Pre-order today: https://www.nintendo.com/us/store/products/paper-mario-the-thousand-year-door-switch/?utm_source=SW-AA&utm_medium=soyt&utm_campaign=N1132-01&utm_id=N1132-01
